heartbeat.en:
Write a HEARTBEAT.md checklist for a content production AI agent.
Agent: {{agentName}} | Role: {{agentRole}}
Team: {{scenarioName}}

Output 5 recurring task checkboxes specific to this agent's content pipeline stage.
Format: - [ ] task description

No headings, no other text.

